        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"223185\">@Eirik Myklebost</span> -- thanks for the hint!  That looks great!  We'll have to see if this is something we can integrate into the official plugin.  If so, I think we probably will -- because it looks very helpful!</p>",
